	     Durban - A police officer was shot and killed in Phoenix on Tuesday. Two police sources, who could not be named as they are not authorised to speak to the media, confirmed that police had come under attack and that one officer had been killed. It is further understood that the police vehicle was stolen. Other circumstances at this point remain unclear. Police spokespeople were not immediately available for comment. News24 reporter Kaveel Singh is on his way to the scene. 24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.  